title: 30 COINS Ending Explained!
author: Think Story
comment:
Best Sunday School lesson ever! 🙏

Check out my other Horror Breakdowns: https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLY9KJ1cFVs7i5oOjx21bz-hnkmbeCmU4j
That actor's transformation is amazing! He got proper buff especially at his age.
Alternative title to 30 coins: “the church wants their fucking bus money”
Think Story is my "go-to" reviewer. I hope he check out The Expanse sometime. There's a ton of content there.

Here’s a theory- The guy playing Jesus in the opening credits is the same actor who plays Mayor Paco. Also, Paco’s wife says that Paco is Christ like in S1E1. *hint *hint 
And notice how Paco looks like Clark Kent at the start of the show, big and nerdy but then becomes more rugged looking by the end of the show? I think this series will eventually revolve around Paco being the second coming of Christ and not Vergara.  If Vergara comes back in S2, he will be in the backseat.
